  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was staying in Budapest for until 1950.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, because my husband was still a Czechoslovakian, he obtained a pass going back, like, home, and take me with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was after the communist came in, and they started-- the communist when they came in they started to take away the businesses from people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my husband has already in partnership a little business because he was a jeweler.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he started to work, but because it was such a dangerous time that everything will be taken away, and we already had a little son-- that was already in 1947.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we started to think of emigrating before they take everything, but we still left something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then in 1950, that friend of mine who was with me in the working camp, she has got that Swedish passport in time, and she got out of the working camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she came also back to live in the house where we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't tell us, but they came in 1950 to Australia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when, when they arrived, they wrote us a letter that we are sitting under a palm tree, and we are already playing tennis.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everything what was enticing and beautiful, and the climate is fantastic, and we want you to come out here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we are going to send you a-- not passport actually, what was it what they sending this time?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is it called?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They get-- they, they take responsibility that we-- A sponsorship--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sponsoring, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, what happened is we decided to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
